message.content: The likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper are "cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.NE". The paper deals with natural language processing and machine learning techniques for generating questions in Hindi, which falls under the scope of computational linguistics (cs.CL), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also uses semantic and syntactic filters to improve the quality of question generation, which can be related to information retrieval (cs.IR) and natural language understanding (cs.NE).
